pageContext.claim: “California -- off the record, California was saying, ‘Please, can we have the wall?’ This is California. You know, they didn't want the wall. They didn't want the wall. But they wanted the wall, right?”
pageContext.analysis: Trump repeatedly has claimed that San Diego local officials clamored for his border wall. The city council and Republican mayor vocally opposed it, as do local and state officials throughout California including the state's Democratic governor.
